Britain will from next autumn mint andmarket a new bullion coin called the "Britannia" containing oneounce of 24 carat gold, together with bullion coins of smallerdenominations, a Treasury official said.    The new investment coin, to be sold worldwide, willfluctuate in price according to the international price ofgold.    The smaller coins will be in denominations of a half ounce,a quarter ounce and a tenth of an ounce. REUTER&#3;